      1          /**
      2           *  @file
      3           *  @defgroup    CLASS_B
      4           *  @brief            This module implements the interface to configuration, refresh and status
      5           *                          check of Unused pins, with ClassB requirements.
      6           *
      7           *  @details         Handles a configuration, refresh and status check of Unused pins.
      8           *                      It's adding Class B requirement.
      9           *                      SRUnusedPinsConfig__Handler5ms running from Asynch task checks current
     10           *                      status & configuration of pins. If any pin status configuration mismatched
     11           *                      it will trigger SR Exception. Execution of SRUnusedPinsConfig__Handler5ms
     12           *                      is monitored by SRUnusedPinsConfig__Monitor running at 100mS. If
     13           *                      execution of SRUnusedPinsConfig__Handler5ms goes beyond expected
     14           *                      limit it will trigger SR Exception.
     15           *
     16           *  @copyright    Copyright 2022 Whirlpool Corporation.  All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL.
     17           */
     18          //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     19          //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     20          
